00:30:01,022 --> 00:30:02,965
Especially, I think that might have been just reactionary

502
00:30:02,985 --> 00:30:05,568
to having just come off Journey, which is like string bonanza.

503
00:30:05,988 --> 00:30:08,191
And so I thought, you know, I just

