00:30:08,231 --> 00:30:10,574
happened to notice that it was very centered around the brass.

505
00:30:11,214 --> 00:30:12,175
So then the thought occurred to me,

506
00:30:13,057 --> 00:30:15,019
what if I just committed to that?

507
00:30:15,139 --> 00:30:16,380
I've never done that before.

508
00:30:16,741 --> 00:30:18,483
And I remembered an experience that I had.

