516
00:30:45,769 --> 00:30:47,570
a percussionist firing a shotgun.

517
00:30:51,940 --> 00:30:56,985
It's a fully surround, like what you're hearing right now is 16 trumpets in a circle around the audience.

518
00:30:57,805 --> 00:30:59,447
