00:31:24,322 --> 00:31:28,985
Whoever I was walking into Carnegie Hall before hearing this piece was not who left that day.

524
00:31:29,586 --> 00:31:32,248
I've never been hit. It was like a sledgehammer to the face, this piece.

525
00:31:32,328 --> 00:31:38,272
It's 40 minutes long. Here's the full band.

526
00:31:39,753 --> 00:31:42,555
Yeah, I decided not to spend the rest of my talk just letting it play out.

527
00:31:43,796 --> 00:31:45,057
But it's worth seeking out.

528
00:31:45,798 --> 00:31:48,400
And so I thought, what if I did...

529
00:31:49,878 --> 00:31:51,439
A wind ensemble score.

530
00:31:51,619 --> 00:31:54,360
And then my brain went to the next sort of ludicrous conclusion of

531
00:31:54,880 --> 00:31:58,962
what if I called this guy and got his wind ensemble to play it?

